                                                                                <p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Poppins; color: rgb(0, 31, 60); letter-spacing: normal; white-space: normal;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.4px;">Let AstraZeneca heal your portfolio</span><span style="color: rgb(6, 42, 74); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1.38px; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span></p>
