                                                                        <div class="elementor-widget-container">
                                                                            <div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
                                                                                <p class="p1" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: open sans, sans-serif; color: #000000;"><span class="s1" style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;">At over 109 years old, AstraZeneca is one of the oldest existing pharmaceutical companies around. The fact that it is also one of the largest and wealthiest companies of its kind is simply icing on a very profitable cake.</span></p>
                                                                                <p class="p2" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: open sans, sans-serif; color: #000000; min-height: 19px;">&nbsp;</p>
                                                                                <p class="p1" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: open sans, sans-serif; color: #000000;"><span class="s1" style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Astra AB was founded in 1913 in Södertälje, Sweden, by 400 doctors and apothecaries.</span></p>
                                                                                <p class="p2" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: open sans, sans-serif; color: #000000; min-height: 19px;">&nbsp;</p>
                                                                                <p class="p1" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: open sans, sans-serif; color: #000000;"><span class="s1" style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;">AstraZeneca is one of the biggest diversified medical companies. In the fourth quarter, AstraZeneca reported 20% growth in adjusted earnings to $1.07 per share. Sales jumped 11% to $7.41 billion.</span></p>
                                                                                <p class="p2" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: open sans, sans-serif; color:#000000; min-height: 19px;">&nbsp;</p>
                                                                                <p class="p1" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: open sans, sans-serif; color: #000000;"><span class="s1" style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;">AstraZeneca stock has yo-yoed this year as challenges mount for its coronavirus vaccine.</span></p>
                                                                                <p class="p2" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: open sans, sans-serif; color: #000000; min-height: 19px;">&nbsp;</p>
                                                                                <p class="p1" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: open sans, sans-serif; color: #000000;"><span class="s1" style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Now, you too can buy AstraZeneca stock with zero commissions and fees.<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span>
                                                                                </p>
                                                                                <p class="p1" style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; font-family: open sans, sans-serif; color: #000000;"><span class="s1" style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Simply, open an account and start trading AstraZeneca<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>shares with all the advantages
